reviewText: This has got to be one of Marika Roekk's best musical films ever made out of her vast variety of achievements! I highly recommend it to anyone interested in German film history.

The movie is as I remember it. A good quality. The only disappointment I had is that it has no english subtitles, and my German is pretty rusty. But that's my problem, not the DVD's. The delivery was promised for mid-March, but received it nearly a month sooner. Excellent service.
